## TypeOf type

Obtains the TypeScript type of the given runtime Type-checker. Aka [The](./types.the.md)<!-- -->.

**Signature:**

```typescript
type TypeOf<T> = T extends {
    readonly [designType]: infer Q;
}
    ? Q
    : never;
```
